{
  "texts": [
    "Regarding 2ZoneDataCenterHVAC, in Fig. 4 we can see a higher instability of TD3 in the first episodes, and a later better performance against SAC and PPO.",
    "In this environment, SAC again demonstrates early convergence, outperforming PPO in cool and hot climates, and equaling it in the mixed case.",
    "Once the algorithms were trained and reached convergence, they were evaluated during 20 episodes using the best model obtained during training.",
    "Figures 5 and 6 show the results obtained for each environment, considering the metrics already presented in Sect. 5.2: mean rewards per episode, power consumption and comfort violation.",
    "We will analyze the results obtained taking as baseline the performance of both RBCs and random agents (RAND)."
  ]
}